00:20:17,700 --> 00:20:21,220
We currently have only
20 hospice quarters. I'd like to

286
00:20:21,220 --> 00:20:25,010
expand and operate a hospice and
palliative care center for terminal patients.

287
00:20:25,010 --> 00:20:28,110
For terminal patients, sustaining their
condition is our target, not the cure.

288
00:20:28,110 --> 00:20:29,380
And?

289
00:20:29,380 --> 00:20:31,700
We're not a convalescent hospital.

290
