This won't help in our
operations, either.

291
00:20:33,810 --> 00:20:36,660
Must we provide hospice
care for terminal patients?

292
00:20:36,660 --> 00:20:37,890
That's what he's saying.

293
00:20:37,890 --> 00:20:41,040
Our goal as doctors and
for our hospital...

294
00:20:41,040 --> 00:20:42,480
isn't only about treating ailments

295
