303
00:21:06,890 --> 00:21:11,450
And now, we'll feel less guilty about it.

304
00:21:15,110 --> 00:21:17,350
It sounds like a good idea.

305
00:21:17,350 --> 00:21:19,730
It'll be tough work, and the
profits will be unpredictable.

306
00:21:19,730 --> 00:21:21,490
Why is she doing this?

307
00:21:21,490 --> 00:21:22,780
I totally agree.

308
00:21:22,780 --> 00:21:25,830
Chairwoman makes
reckless business decisions.

309
00:21:31,420 --> 00:21:32,850
Unni.

310
00:21:32,850 --> 00:21:35,380
- Dr. Cha is here.
- Is that right?

311
00:21:35,380 --> 00:21:38,080
- Tell him to come see me.
- Okay.

312
00:21:45,700 --> 00:21:46,600
What?

313
00:21:49,440 --> 00:21:51,280
Sorry, I'm late.

314
00:21:52,650 --> 00:21:53,730
What's wrong with this patient?

315
00:21:53,800 --> 00:21:57,100
I examined her, but she's suddenly
experiencing abdominal pains.

316
00:21:57,100 --> 00:21:58,600
Not responding to analgesics, either.

317
00:22:05,350 --> 00:22:06,810
The pain is gone now.

318
00:22:07,930 --> 00:22:09,940
- Pardon?
- How?

319
00:22:12,640 --> 00:22:14,940
You're okay all of a sudden?

320
00:22:14,940 --> 00:22:15,710
Yes.

321
00:22:15,710 --> 00:22:17,450
I told you that...

322
00:22:17,450 --> 00:22:19,250
one minute I'm dying of pain,

323
00:22:19,250 --> 00:22:21,020
then I'm suddenly fine.

324
00:22:25,250 --> 00:22:28,470
Daebak news,
daebak, daebak, daebak.

325
00:22:33,850 --> 00:22:35,340
My apologies.

326
00:22:37,620 --> 00:22:38,870
Dr. Lee.

327
00:22:38,870 --> 00:22:41,870
She has no family history of convulsive
diseases or similar ailments.

328
00:22:41,870 --> 00:22:43,670
Her echocardiogram,
lung and abdomen X-rays,

329
00:22:43,670 --> 00:22:46,910
and CT scans show no
abnormalities, either.

330
00:22:46,910 --> 00:22:48,590
- Well...
- A gastroscopy and

331
00:22:48,590 --> 00:22:50,170
a colonoscopy is
scheduled this afternoon.

332
00:22:50,170 --> 00:22:52,620
Since no abnormalities
were found previously,

333
00:22:52,620 --> 00:22:56,550
we'll run a fecal immunochemical test,
and also a stool culture test.

334
00:22:56,550 --> 00:22:57,380
Dr. Heo, what is it?

335
00:22:57,380 --> 00:22:59,490
What is it you've trying to say?

336
00:22:59,490 --> 00:23:00,910
The thing is...

