00:23:00,910 --> 00:23:03,630
Dr. Cha is at our hospital right now.

338
00:23:03,630 --> 00:23:04,920
What?

339
00:23:04,920 --> 00:23:07,190
Dr. Cha? Right now?

340
00:23:07,190 --> 00:23:08,000
Yes.

341
00:23:08,000 --> 00:23:10,290
Someone saw Dr. Cha at our hospital.

342
00:23:10,290 --> 00:23:13,000
Daebak, daebak. When
did he return from the US?

343
00:23:13,000 --> 00:23:15,720
Then will he be coming
back to our hospital?

344
00:23:15,800 --> 00:23:18,400
I don't know about that,
but he looks even cooler.

345
00:23:18,460 --> 00:23:19,820
He was cool to begin with,

346
00:23:19,820 --> 00:23:21,660
but he's looking
healthier than before,

347
00:23:21,660 --> 00:23:24,120
and super duper charismatic.

348
00:23:24,120 --> 00:23:26,080
Of course he would be, Sunbae.

349
00:23:26,080 --> 00:23:28,990
Dr. Cha's research project
is a huge success.

350
00:23:28,990 --> 00:23:30,970
A big US pharmaceutical company

351
00:23:30,970 --> 00:23:33,130
signed an exclusive
contract for the new drug.

352
00:23:40,310 --> 00:23:42,130
I'll take on this patient.

353
00:23:42,130 --> 00:23:43,260
But she's my patient.

354
00:23:43,260 --> 00:23:45,110
Please let me.

355
00:23:45,110 --> 00:23:47,300
I want to stay busy today.

356
00:23:51,420 --> 00:23:52,760
Are you okay?

